(Bodhicaryāvatāra 5. 108)

iti.

<commentary>kaḥ punar anayor vyatireke doṣaḥ, yenaite yatnena rakṣaṇīye kathite ity āha.

rogopahatasāmarthyo yathā puruṣaḥ sarvakarmasu gamanabhojanādiṣv akarmaṇyo bhavati, tathā smṛtisaṃprajanyābhyāṃ vikalaṃ cittaṃ sarvakarmasu dhyānādhyayanādilakṣaṇeṣu.</commentary>

anayoḥ samudāyābhāve doṣam uktvā pratyekam abhāve kathayitum āha. na vidyate saṃprajanyaṃ yasmiṃs tad asaṃprajanyam. taccittaṃ yasya tasya. śrutacintābhāvanāmayaprajñāpariniṣṭhitaṃ vastu na smaraṇam adhivasati.